    Inferno grabbed Darkmouse and looked deeply into her panicing eyes. 
"Megatron is dead. Kitkat killed him. We must get back to the Royalty so she 
can get her. We must hurry!"

    Megatron slammed down his cold hard fist on the display. They had 
discovered his little secret. No matter.....phase two of the plan would go as 
followed. He wasnt going to let anything stand in his way....and would pave 
over any bot who stood in his way of complete, total, and utter destruction 
of the Autobots.
    "Terrorsaur! Get in here now!"

    Hell Beast saw the on coming fire and rolled out of the way, looked up, 
and saw they had stoped. "Cowards. And Kitkat....dont think you have won, 
because I will have the last laugh. Gremlin, cut that net down and bring the 
body." He said, standing up and walking over to the net. Indeed, Hell Beast 
was going o have the final, and most deserved laugh.

    Black Aracnia, Paralysis, Rampage, and Tankkor, waited on the bridge, and 
watched as Megatron exploded before there eyes. She couldnt belive it, and 
didnt belive it.
    "Alright, Rampage and Tankkor, you go and have a look around for 
Megatron. I want him found....and Inferno and Darkmouse had best return 
soon!"
